{"tid":948072,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人由內向撚改變到成為外向撚？","createTime":"2018-12-19T18:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T21:31:01.000Z","uid":207336,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"86f1c181fe6a7d5ed807302300b3383566d6cdca","tid":948072,"uid":207336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:05:07.000Z","msg":"本身係好慢熱既人，又好被動，人地對我既第一感覺都係好靜唔講野個啲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁既性格真係好難識到朋友，所以我要決心改變自己，起碼主動少少先，唔想再因為自己既被動而失去機會<br />\n<br />\n第一步係改變外在，出街襯下衫，執返正自己個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二步係去一個新環境，學習點樣主動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲係個成功例子？"},{"pid":"f3db0f7889a26acbd664d82944a5ddef62e8f215","tid":948072,"uid":175564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:12:00.000Z","msg":"我見過有人本身係怕人，宜家變得談吐正常。<br />\n其實幾外向嘅人都有內向嘅一面，只不過係唔show 出黎咁解。<br />\n心態好緊要，最緊要唔好怕柒。"},{"pid":"dfa3457db79a7298907bdd4976b86de715693ccb","tid":948072,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:13:45.000Z","msg":"冇 下世努力啲"},{"pid":"01e77feb76706df84a5cf5ed211c74771ea13f2c","tid":948072,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:14:26.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"57be659911118152987b2899cd6df78bf15f66cf","tid":948072,"uid":209140,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:17:02.000Z","msg":"外向變內向就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0f39a3593f4150a76fcac09b0d0bff9dae3104","tid":948072,"uid":37374,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:17:29.000Z","msg":"變到50％左右<br />\n為左溝女同人生，唯有格硬黎<br />\n姐係懶係多野講，其實個心好唔自然"},{"pid":"25cf1d7a7af25de326d39afbbfab96b901866c02","tid":948072,"uid":171686,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"86f1c181fe6a7d5ed807302300b3383566d6cdca","tid":948072,"uid":207336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:05:07.000Z","msg":"本身係好慢熱既人，又好被動，人地對我既第一感覺都係好靜唔講野個啲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁既性格真係好難識到朋友，所以我要決心改變自己，起碼主動少少先，唔想再因為自己既被動而失去機會<br />\n<br />\n第一步係改變外在，出街襯下衫，執返正自己個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二步係去一個新環境，學習點樣主動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲係個成功例子？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:19:18.000Z","msg":"我曾經因為係Band3仔 好內向<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nForm 1 都仲係打機毒撚<br />\n但後來年年考全級第一,<br />\n到Form5 做埋武館入面既Headprefect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尤其是係做Headprefect個陣<br />\n早會集隊,你有特權,有隊兵跟你check人校服<br />\n個種感覺真係喚風換雨,不可一世<br />\n個人真係極度自大<br />\n<br />\n或者你會話Band 3入面考第一個個都係垃圾<br />\n但DSE都有23分考到入大學,土木工程."},{"pid":"938965910751877c8b1174f0a7cfa215411f6166","tid":948072,"uid":153505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:19:22.000Z","msg":"墨水唔夠，好快dead air，唔知點同人打開話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f508f9a69d1fcdd1132f733137186bf11b887332","tid":948072,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c0f39a3593f4150a76fcac09b0d0bff9dae3104","tid":948072,"uid":37374,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:17:29.000Z","msg":"變到50％左右<br />\n為左溝女同人生，唯有格硬黎<br />\n姐係懶係多野講，其實個心好唔自然"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:24:38.000Z","msg":"想知更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1209f3fc55ee1d5dfd78e5906948550b8904299","tid":948072,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:26:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18e0246bb1d92d1e7d9b5d0c8758c45addcd33ee","tid":948072,"uid":84484,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:28:16.000Z","msg":"有，<br />\n以前不嬲勁少同人講野/得幾個朋友 又細膽<br />\n公共環境遇到唔熟既人一定dead air個種毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話題終結者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岀黎社會先開始發掘岀外向既一面<br />\n主要因為識到個朋友<br />\n佢善良同直率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  令我知道可以咁樣待人處事:<br />\n真心同人分享自己當下心情<br />\n見到人地好，大方純粹地祝福別人<br />\n人地有困難 真心簡單咁關心/幫手<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒 都係放開自己個心 <br />\n去同人接觸<br />\n會發覺好多事唔洗得自己一個去面對<br />\n<br />\n但始終本性係內向底 <br />\n間唔中都會有想自己靜下既時候既"},{"pid":"29db74c16196bad3a96a8f5ee1818439b2206a05","tid":948072,"uid":216470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:37:47.000Z","msg":"外表其實其次。執正個樣，但毒撚氣場仲喺度，一樣會仆街。(除非你係靚仔到烚下烚下都俾人話可愛天然呆嗰啲。）<br />\n識講嘢緊要啲。啱啱識嘅唔好怕問多幾條問題，問到有啱傾嘅話題就不妨一路傾落去。<br />\n有啲人係真係會唔夾，冇嘢啱傾就唔好強求，唔好jer住嚟講。人哋一feel到你冇嘢講搵嘢嚟講仲尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a1133bfcb0769ab10bee7ba35adf05589966ef","tid":948072,"uid":84484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:52:56.000Z","msg":"自信、講野 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; 樣<br />\n當然執正個樣都係提升自信既一種<br />\n<br />\n搵唔到話題就講下而家眼前睇到 聽到既事<br />\n廷續翻對上一次既話題又得<br />\n總之唔好緊張 同人分享心態去9up下<br />\n<br />\n另外 睇下書 學下野 進修自己內涵<br />\n因為覺得對方麻麻地 係9up層面停留就夠<br />\n但到左真係遇到夾既，如果你有少少墨水/修養，deep talk落去會好鬼正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n否則只係一個外向既煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3df7b0731cccb72c9ad18894c24545f4ebbca03","tid":948072,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T19:14:41.000Z","msg":"我<br />\n<br />\n但到左嗰時你反而唔會想對方成為你朋友<br />\n<br />\n講左咩自己諗"},{"pid":"cb2fbd15775685a1eb095e72c82766fcfda621f1","tid":948072,"uid":173398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T19:26:16.000Z","msg":"以前個心路歷程就係好似樓主咁<br />\n逼自己變開朗 <br />\n但始終內向底 好容易社交疲勞<br />\n搞搞吓就開始摺返<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最重要係自信 同埋同人講嘢要微笑 <br />\n令人覺得你親切 就好多嘢都會容易啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606fd2b36ee47a16335a2b4c2078e8ac61367adf","tid":948072,"uid":278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T19:28:39.000Z","msg":"你既傾計對象先緊要<br />\n兩個都係內向人<br />\n講兩句都可以話題終結<br />\n結果乜都改變唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以對象要多口水<br />\n先會容易帶動到你講野<br />\n從而俾到信心自己改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9321d18c1e7b87f3872a62cffc29934ee636eb3c","tid":948072,"uid":189932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T19:32:13.000Z","msg":"出國體驗下群下唔同種類嘅人，迫自己多啲參觀下社團活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6e970362e4cbedf439ef873e210ae01980c0d2","tid":948072,"uid":189932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9321d18c1e7b87f3872a62cffc29934ee636eb3c","tid":948072,"uid":189932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T19:32:13.000Z","msg":"出國體驗下群下唔同種類嘅人，迫自己多啲參觀下社團活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T19:32:32.000Z","msg":"上少啲連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0db2c154053b577cd56d7b9bda54bd68c2d200","tid":948072,"uid":175490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86f1c181fe6a7d5ed807302300b3383566d6cdca","tid":948072,"uid":207336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:05:07.000Z","msg":"本身係好慢熱既人，又好被動，人地對我既第一感覺都係好靜唔講野個啲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁既性格真係好難識到朋友，所以我要決心改變自己，起碼主動少少先，唔想再因為自己既被動而失去機會<br />\n<br />\n第一步係改變外在，出街襯下衫，執返正自己個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二步係去一個新環境，學習點樣主動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲係個成功例子？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T19:59:15.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"b6d67b67fcd3a88b4a4866634c9c2fe6376b5960","tid":948072,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T20:06:31.000Z","msg":"冇自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857b7218f0ef42c5e414db837566a55aa63e5baf","tid":948072,"uid":167186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T20:07:42.000Z","msg":"內向撚識返啲內向撚好過<br />\n之前為識朋友扮到好外向<br />\n識耐咗堆外向撚就會覺得好煩<br />\n成撚日約約約<br />\n不停係咁講野 可以求其都r到話題<br />\n心入面係咁諗你可唔可以收聲 靜少少 聽到耳仔痛呀屌<br />\n勁難頂"},{"pid":"1b32f7537502ee84a2fbace8dee0ca386479ea00","tid":948072,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T20:09:54.000Z","msg":"出去試下識人都好，去到咁上下你就會摺返發現自己都係鐘意一個人相處多D"},{"pid":"a4e54ebc9e7baebb53f57ec515ddda706ffd00cb","tid":948072,"uid":197074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T20:15:32.000Z","msg":"我，出左黎做野3年間完全改變左性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學、大學果陣都無乜點主動識朋友同傾計，<br />\n摺埋一二邊做書蟲果類黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出黎做野焗住要social同對客，<br />\n個人active左勁多，<br />\n環境真係改變人好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f6448e648bab8b70845b7abad5f3439d2a5fb6","tid":948072,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:19:04.000Z","msg":"小妹返sale都係咁摺<br />\n真心唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a38fe395dd929de9376327008c4da714fefc728","tid":948072,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c0f39a3593f4150a76fcac09b0d0bff9dae3104","tid":948072,"uid":37374,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:17:29.000Z","msg":"變到50％左右<br />\n為左溝女同人生，唯有格硬黎<br />\n姐係懶係多野講，其實個心好唔自然"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\